#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/metadatatools.rst:71
msgid "Copy Layer Metadata"
msgstr "Kopiraj metapodatke sloja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/metadatatools.rst:74
msgid ""
"Copies metadata from a source layer to a target layer. Any existing metadata"
" in the target layer will be replaced with the metadata from the source "
"layer. This includes all metadata fields, such as history, abstract, and "
"other properties."
msgstr ""
"Kopira metapodatke sa izvornog sloja na ciljni sloj. Svi postojeći "
"metapodaci u ciljnom sloju biće zamenjeni metapodacima izvornog sloja. Ovo "
"uključuje sva polja metapodataka, kao što su istorija, apstrakt i druga "
"svojstva."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/metadatatools.rst:90
